  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluate the safety and efficacy of the GORE® CARDIOFORM ASD Occluder in the percutaneous
      closure of ostium secundum atrial septal defects (ASDs)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective, multicenter, single-arm clinical study comparing outcomes with the
      GORE® CARDIOFORM ASD Occluder to performance goals derived from clinical investigation
      outcomes for devices indicated for ASD closure.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
